model

Class InterestPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.InterestPoint

  • public class InterestPoint
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an interest point within a map, identified by its name, coordinates, and a QR code. It encompasses the evidence and comments associated with this point.
